### Create a court
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/courts
Authorization: Basic admin yourpassword
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pickleball Court 1",
  "type": "Pickleball",
  "operatingHoursStart": "08:00:00",
  "operatingHoursEnd": "20:00:00",
  "maxDaysOut": 7
}

### Get all courts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/courts
Authorization: Basic admin yourpassword

### Generate slots for the court (replace COURT_ID with the id from your POST response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/admin/courts/7193fe90-7b87-4c06-89e0-b7b1956fdd1d/generate-slots
Authorization: Basic admin yourpassword

### Get slots for the court
GET http://localhost:8080/api/courts/7193fe90-7b87-4c06-89e0-b7b1956fdd1d/slots?startDate=2026-04-14&endDate=2026-04-21

### Reserve a slot (replace SLOT_ID with any id from the slots response)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/courts/7193fe90-7b87-4c06-89e0-b7b1956fdd1d/slots/eb87484a-76ad-4e43-9dfd-94efb608b06e/reserve
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookerName": "John",
  "bookerEmail": "thejohnnysavoy@gmail.com"
}
